socket.on("connection", function (socket) { console.log("Client connected."); }); axios.defaults.withCredentials = true; axios .get("http://localhost:3005/dashboard", { withCredentals: true, }) .then((res) => { dispatch(userData(res.data.info)); setFriends(res.data.info.friends); }) .catch((e) => console.log(e)); }, []); const openConversation = (userId) => { setOpenChats(!openChats); axios .get("http://localhost:3005/chats?userId=" + userId) .then(function (response) { // handle success dispatch(showMessages(response.data.info.messages)); dispatch(chatData(response.data.info)); }) .catch(function (error) { // handle error console.log(error); }); }; const openTab = (tab) => { setTab(tab); }; const filteredFriends = friends.filter((res) => res.messages.length > 0);
